Amanda Aday https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Amanda_Aday 0 Amanda Lee Aday (born January 21, 1981) is an American actress. Is best known for her recurring role as Dora Mae Dreifuss on the first season of the 2003–2005 HBO series Carnivàle. Amanda_Lee_Aday ( born January_21 , 1981 ) is an_American_actress .
